Well located unit.  Nice and close to Strathfield Private Hospital and surrounding facilities.  Nice and close to a good Italian restaurant as well. The owner went out his way to get the unit ready for us after a black out neatly delayed our check in.  The unit has has everything you need, but a few extras such as bath mats, tissues, milk etc would have been good.  Batteries in the remotes probably need replacing as well.  Would  certainly stay here again.
